{"tid":1212232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"情況急轉直下 trump叫香港自己work things out","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T18:34:56.000Z","uid":76705,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"28eb27401e9b4d5d90e34ff386a81d28388db4b6","tid":1212232,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:45:56.000Z","msg":"WASHINGTON (Reuters) - U.S. President Donald Trump said on Wednesday he is sure <span style=\"color: red;\">China and Hong Kong will be able to work things out</span> after mass protests against an extradition bill that would allow people to be sent to mainland China for trial descended into chaos.<br />\n<br />\nTrump本身少氣又唔like香港人<br />\n單官司輸咗咁多錢後就肯定更憎香港人<br />\n而出到聲支持香港個Nancy Pelosi重要係trump每日開炮民主黨眾議院議長<br />\n加上咁大單野都只係叫你地自己同中國work things out<br />\nTrump隨時賣撚咗香港比中國都有可能<br />\n香港人快啲做好兩手準備<br />\n死因隨時唔只係中共777 重包括trump同鄭家純羅康瑞<br />\n<br />\n詳細：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/23827/%E6%8F%AD%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%88%87%E9%84%AD%E5%AE%B6%E7%B4%94%E7%BE%85%E5%BA%B7%E7%91%9E%E5%8F%8D%E7%9B%AE%E8%88%8A%E5%B8%B3-%E7%BE%85-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%91%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A6%82%E5%AE%B6%E5%B8%B8%E4%BE%BF%E9%A3%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F23827%2F%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25B4%2594%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%259B%25AE%25E8%2588%258A%25E5%25B8%25B3-%25E7%25BE%2585-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E9%25A3%25AF&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=9f75601c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/23827/%E6%8F%AD%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%88%87%E9%84%AD%E5%AE%B